msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:278
msgid "Browser storage"
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:279
msgid "A copy of your recent messages and conversation data is cached in your browser (IndexedDB) for faster loading. This data stays on your device and is not shared. You can clear it by clearing your browser data."
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:286
msgid "Video links (YouTube, Vimeo, etc.) may load embedded players directly from those services, which allows them to collect data about your visit."
