msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:298
msgid "GIF images are loaded directly from Giphy's servers (media.giphy.com) when displayed in messages, which may receive your IP address."
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:302
msgid "Sticker images are loaded directly from Stipop's servers (img.stipop.io) when displayed in messages, which may receive your IP address."
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:306
msgid "Group voice and video calls are routed through a cloud service to connect participants. Private one-on-one calls are established directly between users."
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:310
msgid "Real-time message delivery is handled through a cloud server (cloud.better-messages.com). Your messages are encrypted in transit and pass through this server for instant delivery."
