msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:331
msgid "This site may use AI-powered chat bots. When you interact with an AI bot, your messages in that conversation are sent to the AI service provider (such as OpenAI, Anthropic, or Google) to generate responses."
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:338
msgid "Data retention and your rights"
msgstr ""

#: addons/privacy.php:339
msgid "Your messages are stored as long as your account is active. You can request an export of your messaging data or request deletion of your messages through the privacy tools provided by this site (Tools → Export Personal Data / Erase Personal Data). When messages are erased, the content is replaced with a placeholder to preserve conversation context for other participants."
msgstr ""

